  "$comment": "avenOS brand design system — single source of truth for vibe views (shadow-DOM) and a mirror of the app's app.css @theme tokens. Values are codified from the canonical reference card (GoalsDashboard 'cashflow / your climb'): rounded-xl cards, p-6 padding, gap-6 sections, 11px tracked uppercase eyebrows, dark-blue ink. The StyleEngine flattens these into CSS custom properties on :host (e.g. `text` -> --text). Keep names in sync with app.css. To retheme the whole vibe layer, edit here.",

